<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, January 2 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Saturday closed at 1531.79 points, up 0.74
points from that of Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 719,086 shares exchanged hands in 421 turns and the
turnover stood at 2.86 billion rials (about 477,000 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 14 companies made gains while those of 10 others
declined. 
</P>
