people's advice before a policy is going to be launched, just like
what is done in many Western countries," he said.
</P>
<P>
Sun was addressing to complaints from some overseas investors
on the capriciousness and lack of transparency in policy-making.
</P>
<P>
One of the leading tasks for the Ministry of Foreign Trade and
Economic Cooperation (MOFTEC) this year is to utilize more
