<HEADLINE> Xinhua World News Summary 1:00 GMT January 3 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING -- Total exports of China in 1998 were valued at 180
billion U.S. dollars, Zhang Xiang, Vice-Minister of Foreign Trade
and Economic Cooperation (MOFTEC), has predicted.(China-Exports)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
